<deviceset name="MIC" prefix="MK" urn="urn:adsk.eagle:component:6731905/1">
<description>&lt;h3&gt;Microphone&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Omni-directional electret microphones - one through-hole, the other SMD.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://cdn.sparkfun.com/datasheets/Sensors/Sound/CEM-C9745JAD462P2.54R.pdf"&gt;Datasheet&lt;/a&gt; (through-hole mic)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.challengeelectronics.com/downloads/microphones/omni_directional/CEM-OB6018-3EAD443C43MR.pdf"&gt;Datasheet&lt;/a&gt; (SMD mic)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;SparkFun Products&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.sparkfun.com/products/8635"&gt;PTH Electret Microphone&lt;/a&gt; (COM-08635)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.sparkfun.com/products/9964"&gt;SparkFun Electret Microphone Breakout &lt;/a&gt; (BOB-09964)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.sparkfun.com/products/12651"&gt;Digital Sandbox&lt;/a&gt; (DEV-12651)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.sparkfun.com/products/12642"&gt;SparkFun Sound Detector&lt;/a&gt; (SEN-12642)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SMD Microphone&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.sparkfun.com/products/retired/10653"&gt;SparkFun Voice Recorder Breakout - ISD1932&lt;/a&gt; (BOB-10653)&lt;/li&gt;</description>
